Human

Appearance

Humans are standard run of the mill people with traits like real humans.

Naming Convention

Humans probably have the widest variety of names across Erendia, but for the most part, they have common names and rarely use titles as part of their identity.

Biology

Human biology is the same in fiction as it is in the real world, save for the fact humans are capable of weaving magic.

Geography

Humans know no bounds, and have spread far and wide across Erendia establishing settlements and building civilizations. They are regarded as peculiar in that sense by those with longer lifespans, as it seems Humans are driven to accomplish as much as possible in their short lives.
